of the squid, it's called the squid giant axon

22
00:01:30,869 --> 00:01:36,281
it is giant, it is from here to here, it's a very thick axon,

23
00:01:36,977 --> 00:01:42,664
in our brain, our axon are very thin something of the order of a 1μm

24
